reviewText: I love all of Leslie's walks.  Keeps you in shape no matter how much time you have to spend.
I like her walking tapes and own just about everyone that is out there!

I actually workout with Leslie. I can do mini walks! I turn on the DVD and all of a sudden I've gone a mile in my office. This is perfect for me. I have very low motivation to exercise but I can do this. So glad I got this DVD! I'm losing weight and getting in shape, too!
